  "content": "<p data-pid=\"24GQ8X4m\">先分析一下论题，关键字：高三、复习、高效。</p><p data-pid=\"79BExLxL\">想要满足这几个条件，我的回答只有一个</p><h2>间隔重复<sup data-text=\"【理论】Study smarter, NOT longer. 你需要间隔重复！\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57020308\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>，降维打击！</h2><p data-pid=\"SzVpdOeg\">先介绍一下自己，我是学委叶哥叶峻峣，18 年全国一卷理科考生，现就读于哈尔滨工业大学（深圳）计算机。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-94ecc8103a8c034a45b6a4fc449da287_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1770\" data-rawheight=\"368\" data-original-token=\"v2-1906103ac2b9e3c1795b0c9a83b8725b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c9b37ecfc644fc52af9c9a6645da79c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1770\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-94ecc8103a8c034a45b6a4fc449da287_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1770&#39; height=&#39;368&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1770\" data-rawheight=\"368\" data-original-token=\"v2-1906103ac2b9e3c1795b0c9a83b8725b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c9b37ecfc644fc52af9c9a6645da79c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1770\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-94ecc8103a8c034a45b6a4fc449da287_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-94ecc8103a8c034a45b6a4fc449da287_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f89c50ee9bbc98e2891ff374482c4fb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"641\" data-rawheight=\"721\" data-original-token=\"v2-4bb4c8a12b46cf44bd889d7e57cdec65\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b94e8068c788e36176852de6e8a8fbb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"641\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4f89c50ee9bbc98e2891ff374482c4fb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;641&#39; height=&#39;721&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"641\" data-rawheight=\"721\" data-original-token=\"v2-4bb4c8a12b46cf44bd889d7e57cdec65\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b94e8068c788e36176852de6e8a8fbb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"641\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4f89c50ee9bbc98e2891ff374482c4fb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f89c50ee9bbc98e2891ff374482c4fb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"OO1NgxIH\">接下来我要向大家介绍的，是我从 17 年 4 月使用至今的复习方法，也是助我在高三一年中逆袭 157 分<sup data-text=\"你想知道如何高考逆袭吗？ 看我用 Anki 从本一线上涨 157 分！\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/41568928\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>的复习神器！</p><h2>复习方法：间隔重复</h2><h2>复习工具：Anki</h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-665afcd42b02975679792a9d67f61ebf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"466\" data-rawheight=\"335\" data-original-token=\"v2-d52a80230c5f62bcac3a47e2d28b9668\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f680c023e7e370af4d6305515e80144_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"466\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-665afcd42b02975679792a9d67f61ebf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;466&#39; height=&#39;335&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"466\" data-rawheight=\"335\" data-original-token=\"v2-d52a80230c5f62bcac3a47e2d28b9668\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f680c023e7e370af4d6305515e80144_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"466\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-665afcd42b02975679792a9d67f61ebf_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-665afcd42b02975679792a9d67f61ebf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"22isidGv\">啥？？？啥和啥啊？我读书少可别骗我！</p><p data-pid=\"ZwIcQx9a\">不急不急，让我慢慢道来~</p><h2>什么是间隔重复？</h2><p data-pid=\"Ntucq_Zh\">这就要从遗忘曲线说起了。遗忘曲线，是我们学习之后遗忘的速度。如果用一个式子来描述这条曲线，那么我会用这个式子<sup data-text=\"记忆的两个组成成分\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/179076885\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup>：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"217\" data-original-token=\"v2-0962366c90f2c5c46006c4ee3da80b14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-21947eb6b0adee237d139d2428b9bf2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;217&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"217\" data-original-token=\"v2-0962366c90f2c5c46006c4ee3da80b14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-21947eb6b0adee237d139d2428b9bf2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"hmM3KzF7\">R 表示我们记住一个知识的概率，t 是离上次学习过去的时间（天数），S 是我们对一个知识的熟练程度。</p><p data-pid=\"bSgber_E\">大家都是高三学生了，总知道这个式子的含义吧，让我们把它画出来试试：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-22af479fa25a09ae7115f4a8ab5223df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1208\" data-rawheight=\"671\" data-original-token=\"v2-2beec9dcb2e708b4494fccf692cfa76f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cd35c04940c8c70e71c1ba9bcb064af_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1208\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-22af479fa25a09ae7115f4a8ab5223df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1208&#39; height=&#39;671&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1208\" data-rawheight=\"671\" data-original-token=\"v2-2beec9dcb2e708b4494fccf692cfa76f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cd35c04940c8c70e71c1ba9bcb064af_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1208\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-22af479fa25a09ae7115f4a8ab5223df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-22af479fa25a09ae7115f4a8ab5223df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"GrLWKKUX\">这幅图很形象的点出了我们遗忘的特点：<b>先快后慢</b></p><p data-pid=\"7HjyqMeA\">重点来了，我们为啥要复习？</p><h2>为了对抗遗忘</h2><p data-pid=\"Rd8QZLDa\">怎么对抗？看看这幅图说不定就懂了</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c7641b0fad9d37beb6cacec419b7470c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1197\" data-rawheight=\"672\" data-original-token=\"v2-9995f90aeb966a4a5eebbb5a20e03d82\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-af67b477da8f07caaddfc9e631aadae4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1197\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c7641b0fad9d37beb6cacec419b7470c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1197&#39; height=&#39;672&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1197\" data-rawheight=\"672\" data-original-token=\"v2-9995f90aeb966a4a5eebbb5a20e03d82\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-af67b477da8f07caaddfc9e631aadae4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1197\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c7641b0fad9d37beb6cacec419b7470c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c7641b0fad9d37beb6cacec419b7470c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Sk6bJeSh\">发现规律了吗？当我们去复习时，不仅提高了记住知识的概率，还让遗忘曲线变平缓了。</p><p data-pid=\"Athphgg8\">变平缓意味着什么？忘得更慢了，记得更久了！</p><p data-pid=\"D00eD4N5\">回顾之前的式子：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"217\" data-original-token=\"v2-0962366c90f2c5c46006c4ee3da80b14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-21947eb6b0adee237d139d2428b9bf2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;217&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"217\" data-original-token=\"v2-0962366c90f2c5c46006c4ee3da80b14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-21947eb6b0adee237d139d2428b9bf2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-fe88310833c5a1f60adc19ffbac8bb4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"cm_o1XgU\">曲线变平缓反映在这里，那就是 S 变大了！S 是什么？我们对知识的熟练度！合理的复习可以提高我们对知识的熟练度，这很重要，划重点哦~</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-270da3ab5640ebf95710de5054b5263e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-f77c9de95c5b7fa7b32d0e1e112dcb40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ea31c6e0b385698299984e1a5be77a86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-270da3ab5640ebf95710de5054b5263e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1207&#39; height=&#39;679&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1207\" data-rawheight=\"679\" data-original-token=\"v2-f77c9de95c5b7fa7b32d0e1e112dcb40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ea31c6e0b385698299984e1a5be77a86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1207\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-270da3ab5640ebf95710de5054b5263e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-270da3ab5640ebf95710de5054b5263e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"j1myaYLj\">那么怎么规划我们的合理复习呢？ <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/3459e77c59ce07f86f49754576eecadc\" data-hash=\"3459e77c59ce07f86f49754576eecadc\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$3459e77c59ce07f86f49754576eecadc\">@寒色</a> 高赞的答主是通过表格加日期的方式来规划复习的，这里我给大家介绍一个更牛掰的工具——Anki</p><h2>先放两张图让大家看看 Anki 的厉害之处：</h2><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ffa93924ac6237d52d8120dc6ebd5560_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1002\" data-rawheight=\"1079\" data-original-token=\"v2-9ab7ea348a83bb0e990713fd557a2f48\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8597b005c96d32228037ee82636598c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1002\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ffa93924ac6237d52d8120dc6ebd5560_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1002&#39; height=&#39;1079&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1002\" data-rawheight=\"1079\" data-original-token=\"v2-9ab7ea348a83bb0e990713fd557a2f48\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8597b005c96d32228037ee82636598c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1002\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ffa93924ac6237d52d8120dc6ebd5560_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ffa93924ac6237d52d8120dc6ebd5560_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcf82e13305007e7b29ecd81bed7923b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"810\" data-original-token=\"v2-38c9e8973f35f2efeed4d0700ec39bbc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-95710f024b38e8bccd6f1aac0e84a2d0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-dcf82e13305007e7b29ecd81bed7923b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1440&#39; height=&#39;810&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1440\" data-rawheight=\"810\" data-original-token=\"v2-38c9e8973f35f2efeed4d0700ec39bbc\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-95710f024b38e8bccd6f1aac0e84a2d0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1440\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-dcf82e13305007e7b29ecd81bed7923b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcf82e13305007e7b29ecd81bed7923b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"i7-z_jW0\">高三一年，我和同学用手机+电脑，做出了 1 万 5 千多张复习卡片<sup data-text=\"史上最“全”「Anki高考」牌组整理完毕\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/38507330\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup>，覆盖语文、英语、物理、化学、生物 5 大学科，并且每张卡片都由 Anki 安排复习，帮我和同学节省了大量复习时间！</p><h2>怎么用 Anki？</h2><p data-pid=\"kt3-DUJU\">使用 Anki 只需要两步：制卡 + 复习</p><p data-pid=\"y7RXt8b6\">制卡，手机电脑都可以，以安卓手机为例：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/zvideo/1184414307633344512\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\"></a><p data-pid=\"nSwtTPm0\">制作好卡片就可以复习啦：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/zvideo/1184414821624340480\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\"></a><p data-pid=\"2rowQ-5a\">是不是很简单？给大家看看我高三时使用 Anki 的统计数据：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b662ae3692e7853af685e32fe037def0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-original-token=\"v2-b83b822764545c69d4ea7164b24f375a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b07905933f6fbed2469f96f84557ffe3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b662ae3692e7853af685e32fe037def0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;1280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-original-token=\"v2-b83b822764545c69d4ea7164b24f375a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b07905933f6fbed2469f96f84557ffe3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b662ae3692e7853af685e32fe037def0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b662ae3692e7853af685e32fe037def0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"WZTihQJD\">一天复习 500+ 知识点，每个小知识点平均只花 7 秒钟！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-75041fce177cf9f9a3f852ed42847f73_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-75041fce177cf9f9a3f852ed42847f73_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;634&#39; height=&#39;542&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"634\" data-rawheight=\"542\" data-original-token=\"v2-b7bc9d68cc3bad4191d13f9c9ee9231d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a641a697f7c377f601ead979040ecf_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"634\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-75041fce177cf9f9a3f852ed42847f73_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-75041fce177cf9f9a3f852ed42847f73_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"IMhHWBg6\">每张卡片都分为正面和背面，背面会显示答案和反馈选项。通过自己给自己的复习打分，Anki 会优化下一次复习的时间，最终保证每天都能记住<b> 90%</b> 以上的知识。</p><p data-pid=\"Ce-f9p06\">什么概念呢？如果我每天将我要复习的材料制作成 50 张卡片放进 Anki 复习，300 天后我一共制作了 15000 张卡片，而 Anki 可以帮助我至少记住 15000 * 90% = 13500 张卡片！再也不用担心考试忘记自己学会的内容了！</p><h2>复习压力不会太大吗？</h2><p data-pid=\"3HC2yOfD\">Anki 的算法<sup data-text=\"Anki 算法与术语浅谈\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/42921090\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"5\">[5]</sup>是符合遗忘曲线的，也就是说，如果你每一次复习都记住了，那么 Anki 会认为你对这张卡片的熟练度越来越高，遗忘的越来越慢，就给你安排越来越长的间隔，把复习时间留给新加入的卡片：<br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-51f2bcd362a672a361baf0e8b0d3c128_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1002\" data-rawheight=\"1079\" data-original-token=\"v2-233a145b3628fa8b672584fe7e254943\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6487328973be6cdbb9b7cb3a994176c2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1002\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-51f2bcd362a672a361baf0e8b0d3c128_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1002&#39; height=&#39;1079&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1002\" data-rawheight=\"1079\" data-original-token=\"v2-233a145b3628fa8b672584fe7e254943\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6487328973be6cdbb9b7cb3a994176c2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1002\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-51f2bcd362a672a361baf0e8b0d3c128_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-51f2bcd362a672a361baf0e8b0d3c128_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"sWY9IZih\">看到了吗？学习 1 次，复习 4 次，间隔就安排到了 2.5 个月之后。而且每次复习的时间很短，我总共花在这张卡片上的时间只有 28 秒。</p><h2>真的有用吗？有别的同学的例子吗？</h2><p data-pid=\"1V4iGhtm\">放心，这里除了逆袭 150+ 分的我，还有——</p><p data-pid=\"Ey-U8ab3\">北京前 300 名的大佬：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/165108643\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-19066519c9dc3d91ecc404ef97d9ee34_bh.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4474\" data-image-height=\"2975\" class=\"internal\">Shom：前2%考生中提升 800 名+？Anki 与我的提分之路</a><p data-pid=\"_oAD4Qno\">还有还有：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/108313018\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">ACRL：我的anki高考自救之路</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/161332209\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e28788aa165bc57b76b0c33651d9d5d7_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2056\" data-image-height=\"1299\" class=\"internal\">忘先生：无法被复制的125天anki增分之路</a><p data-pid=\"c9frnpzO\">哎呀，这里的位置太小，排不下了，2333</p><h2>好像很有用，该怎么上手？</h2><p data-pid=\"OAZi779t\">放心，Anki 我也用了 3 年多，已经编写了一套完整的入门教程：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"kPtKdom9\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784948\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 0 章 可有可无的话</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"0L_HuyW5\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784949\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.1 Anki X 高考</a></li><li data-pid=\"mbmbTCjh\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784950\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.2 这本书值得读吗？</a></li><li data-pid=\"bgedvpDX\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784951\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.3 前言</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"h08kFvle\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784952\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 1 章 了解 Anki X 高考</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"3qQupipW\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784658\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.1 Anki 是什么？</a></li><li data-pid=\"UfPSre7O\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784659\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.2 高考是什么？</a></li><li data-pid=\"pYU6TtsW\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784660\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.3 为什么用 Anki 备战高考？</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"7531u649\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784661\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 2 章 准备工作</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"zOkPustB\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784662\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">2.1 Windows/Mac</a></li><li data-pid=\"lXnsHMFi\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784663\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">2.2 Android</a></li><li data-pid=\"Mi5FLRc2\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784664\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">2.3 iOS</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"LNJ04Z5D\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784665\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 3 章 基础用法</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"OnLQRdAd\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784666\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">3.1 导入卡片</a></li><li data-pid=\"VIsGN5fI\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784667\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">3.2 制定计划</a>（内含多级牌