/784683\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">5.5 自律与规划</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"wELj6_Rr\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784956\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">结语</a></li></ul><p data-pid=\"DCxgDUwl\">而且还无偿分享了我和同学高三做的大部分精华笔记：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/column/c_1273994778548252672\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b6546a28845e426a25b971ce7fcab919_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"200\" data-image-height=\"200\" class=\"internal\">Anki高考牌组</a><p data-pid=\"BRu8wdm_\">大家可以先看看几张图片，饱饱眼福：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9014d4c45bc53eccd499ab147a8f7dcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1192\" data-rawheight=\"533\" data-original-token=\"v2-da5b24a5625363379dad46c0cc89226f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a4e2b3eab480638788a49ef0d9326d8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1192\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9014d4c45bc53eccd499ab147a8f7dcd_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1192&#39; height=&#39;533&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1192\" data-rawheight=\"533\" data-original-token=\"v2-da5b24a5625363379dad46c0cc89226f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a4e2b3eab480638788a49ef0d9326d8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1192\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9014d4c45bc53eccd499ab147a8f7dcd_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9014d4c45bc53eccd499ab147a8f7dcd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"h